snippet.title: Yearning: A Gay Story (YAGS) Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Yearning: A Gay Story (YAGS) is a visual novel game about being gay, coming out, meeting people, and making friends. See http://yags.bobcgames.com for more information or to download the game for free!

Game trailer created in RenPy! More information here: http://bobcgames.com/blog/?p=233
